high_descs: Turn around, cross the room and turn left to face the white, round table.
Pick the potato on the left up from the table.
Go left and then left again to face the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick the potato up.
Go to the right and face the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the bin
Pick up a potato from the table
Move to the microwave to the left of the fridge
Heat up the potato in the microwave and retrieve it
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Place the potato inside the fridge and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go straight back to the white table.
Pick up the potato on the right side of the table.
Carry the potato and turn to the left. Go past the island and find the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave and turn it on. Take the potato out of the microwave and shut the door.
Carry the potato and turn around and go left to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the potato inside. Shut the fridge.
